Achievements.Name: A warm welcome
Achievements.Description: Start the game.

Achievements.Name: Enjoy the silence
Achievements.Description: "Calm down" the commentator.

Achievements.Name: First insight
Achievements.Description: Complete the interactive tutorial in any discipline (single player).

Achievements.Name: Ultimate understanding
Achievements.Description: Complete the interactive tutorial in each discipline (single player).

Achievements.Name: Comeback
Achievements.Description: Win a Fencing bout after trailing at least 5:9 points (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Close call
Achievements.Description: At Fencing, score a point on a simultaneous attack (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Flawless victory
Achievements.Description: Win a Fencing bout without getting hit (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Sniper
Achievements.Description: Hit the bullseye 8 times in a single Archery event (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Head in the clouds
Achievements.Description: Trampolining: Achieve perfect timing for each of the first 5 jumps (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Acrophobia
Achievements.Description: Win at trampolining without making use of intermediate jumps (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Purist
Achievements.Description: Win a mountainbike race without performing tricks (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Firm in the saddle
Achievements.Description: Win a mountainbike race without crashing (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Wheel on fire
Achievements.Description: Perform a perfect start at Mountain Biking (single player).

Achievements.Name: Down to earth
Achievements.Description: Crash 3 times in a mountainbike race and still win (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Trick cyclist
Achievements.Description: Mountain Biking: Combine an advanced trick with another trick during 1 jump and land(single player).

Achievements.Name: Versatile
Achievements.Description: Perform all basic tricks and tweaks within one mountainbike race (single player).

Achievements.Name: Perfect performance I
Achievements.Description: Swimming: Perform a perfect start, turn and finish within one race (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Perfect performance II
Achievements.Description: Triple Jump: Achieve perfect hop, step, jump and posture within 1 attempt (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Perfect performance III
Achievements.Description: High Jump: Run up with perfect steps only and maintain a perfect posture within 1 attempt (normal).

Achievements.Name: Awesome angle
Achievements.Description: Attain a perfect angle 3 times in a row in a Javelin event (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Terrific timing
Achievements.Description: Throw with perfect timing 3 times in a row in any Throwing event (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Changed my mind
Achievements.Description: 400m Sprint: Achieve best intermediate time but finish in 4th place (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Tough luck
Achievements.Description: Hurdles: Be 1st before the last hurdle, crash into only this last one and lose (single player).

Achievements.Name: Cool running
Achievements.Description: Win a 100m sprint with a Jamaican team and beat the world record (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Tour de force
Achievements.Description: Get awarded with 5 rewards at once (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Gold collector
Achievements.Description: Obtain a gold medal in each discipline (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: You must be cheating!
Achievements.Description: Break the world record 3 times in the same discipline (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: You rule the world!
Achievements.Description: Set up a new world record in each discipline (single player, normal).

Achievements.Name: Run like hell
Achievements.Description: Run a total of 6666 meters in the career.

Achievements.Name: Bigger than Ben
Achievements.Description: Accumulate a jumping height of 9630cm in a career (Pole Vault, High Jump).

Achievements.Name: First steps
Achievements.Description: Win your first gold medal and buy your first skill in a career.

Achievements.Name: One at a time
Achievements.Description: Buy one skill for each sport in a career.

Achievements.Name: Specialized
Achievements.Description: Buy all skills for any sport in a career.

Achievements.Name: Skillful
Achievements.Description: Buy 30 different skills in a career.

Achievements.Name: Warm up
Achievements.Description: Level up 1 skill to level 3 in a career.

Achievements.Name: Gifted
Achievements.Description: Level up 7 skills to level 3 in a career.

Achievements.Name: Jack of all trades
Achievements.Description: Buy all skills and fully upgrade each in a career.

Achievements.Name: Specialist
Achievements.Description: Win all special challenges in a career.

Achievements.Name: Who's the boss?
Achievements.Description: Win all One On Ones in a career.

Achievements.Name: Go Pro
Achievements.Description: Qualify for the Pro League (career).

Achievements.Name: Pearl Cup
Achievements.Description: Win the Pearl Cup (career).

Achievements.Name: Advanced athlete
Achievements.Description: Qualify for the Champion League (career).

Achievements.Name: Junior Champion
Achievements.Description: Obtain gold in each event of the Junior League (career).

Achievements.Name: World Tour Finals
Achievements.Description: Win the World Tour Finals (career).

Achievements.Name: Level 5
Achievements.Description: Reach Level 5 with your team in a career.

Achievements.Name: Level 20
Achievements.Description: Reach Level 20 with your team in a career.

Achievements.Name: Level 35
Achievements.Description: Reach Level 35 with your team in a career.

Achievements.Name: Level 50
Achievements.Description: Reach Level 50 with your team in a career.

Achievements.Name: What's next?
Achievements.Description: Win a gold medal in each event of a career.
